Distribution . On reefs from the Red Sea to Madagascar in the west, to Guam and the Tonga Islands in the east, including tropical Australia as far south as the Capricorn Channel, Queensland, and as far north as Okinawa, Japan . Previous records, possibly as far east as Kwajalein (AH
Clark 1921 b
;
Meyer & Macurda 1980
;
Zmarzly 1985
;
Stevens 1989
) may be based on incorrectly identified specimens. Depth range: shoreline possibly to 73 m (AH
Clark 1941
); most specimens have been collected in <
30 m .
